02:17.643 --> 02:19.545
Never mind then. We've got work to do.

02:19.545 --> 02:20.711
Now remember, just because

02:20.711 --> 02:22.014
the network is forcing me

02:22.014 --> 02:23.549
to put you on camera,

02:23.549 --> 02:24.783
