02:26.151 --> 02:27.752
You still have to keep the set free

02:27.752 --> 02:29.854
from all ghosts.

02:29.854 --> 02:31.088
Am I understood?

02:31.088 --> 02:32.223
Crystal.

02:32.223 --> 02:33.891
My TV show premieres tonight,

02:33.891 --> 02:36.562
