02:38.329 --> 02:40.799
I'm not going to do any readings

02:40.799 --> 02:42.867
or talk to any ghosts.

02:42.867 --> 02:44.902
Today I'm just a regular gal

02:44.902 --> 02:46.337
going to get her hair done.

02:46.337 --> 02:47.939
Excuse me, Miss?

02:47.939 --> 02:50.008
