03:34.086 --> 03:36.054
A hair genius...

03:36.054 --> 03:38.257
nay... savant.

03:38.257 --> 03:39.557
Remember!

03:39.557 --> 03:40.658
It's not the haircut

03:40.658 --> 03:42.227
